				<div class="comment-body"><p>The results released are what&#8217;s required by the WSFS Constitution, and is what we mean by &#8220;detailed statistics.&#8221; For the raw nominating data (anonymized), you need to contact this year&#8217;s Hugo Award Administrators, a link to which is on the 2015 Hugo Awards page. You can also contact them through the Sasquan web site staff/committee page.</p>
</div>

