				<div class="comment-body"><p>Congratulations to Vox Day for manipulating the awards so the &#8220;true fans&#8221; would burn it down.</p>
<p>What percentage of the people voting the No Award slate even gave the nominees fair consideration?</p>
<p>(my first thought was to wonder how many of the No Award ballots were actually valid, considering the convention&#8217;s endorsement of anti-Puppy activity, but I was told by a Sad Puppy supporter that despite the convention&#8217;s actions, the people counting the votes are honest).</p>
</div>

